<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <p class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
            Enter your name below to join the quiz!
        </p>
        <form
            class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1"
            style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
        >
        <div class="form-group {{# if errors }}has-error{{/ if }}">
                <label class="control-label" for="player-name">
                    {{errors}}
                </label>
                <input
                    class="form-control"
                    type="text"
                    name="player-name"
                    value="{{name}}"
                    placeholder="Enter your name"
                />
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-primary form-control">
                Join!
            </button>
        </form>
        <p class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
            If you have no idea why you are here: first check to make sure
            there isn't some bloke in front of you talking about websockets, if
            there is, listen to him; if there isn't, well, do whatever you 
            want.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
